text: anak teangnoh kuchea anak del a l laoh ban changaoulobangheanh . dau che neah chaur anak( mou ham meat) anouvotd tam kar changaoulobangheanh robsa puokke choh . chaur anak pol tha khnhom min teamtear kamrei pi puok anak leu kar phsaapv phsaay( kompir kuor an) nih laey . vea kmeanoavei krawpi kar romluk samreab piphp teangoasa noh laey
